txt.en: One or more items have been placed in your Housing Escrow. This can happen because you have abandoned or lost a house with decorations or items in chests there. It can also happen if a change was made to the type and number of hooks in your house.\n\nTo retrieve these items, visit an Escrow Broker and choose the option to view your escrow. Items can only be removed from escrow. Those items must be retrieved within [placeholder] of entering escrow or they will be lost.
